    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (cooking for kids? Skip the chilli!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your <strong>salsa</strong></p>",
